{"tid":495972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大吉利是】新人花$4.2萬佈置成咁 結婚禮堂變「靈堂」","createTime":"2017-12-11T08:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T08:49:55.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5672d42d4f97341372aeb4b8f5679036b729decb","tid":495972,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>【大吉利是】新人花$4.2萬佈置成咁 結婚禮堂變「靈堂」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/10/3501838/20171210chinaR_06e_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F3501838%2F20171210chinaR_06e_w.mp4&d=OZLboJ8a3aGlrRIfUsiPBE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=282f27df\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/10/3501838/20171210chinaR_06e_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910423_41fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910423_41fa.jpg&h=b88ec5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個人都希望有一個難忘婚禮。安徽合肥一對新人舉行婚禮，更特意找來一家婚宴公司，花3.6萬元(人民幣‧下同；約4.2萬港元)，佈置會場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910425_e15a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910425_e15a.jpg&h=ea846533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910426_8655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910426_8655.jpg&h=d7d47f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910427_4d32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910427_4d32.jpg&h=c466123f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910428_516a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910428_516a.jpg&h=ec9be4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910429_812e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910429_812e.jpg&h=233f2fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910431_9629.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910431_9629.jpg&h=c5e83ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171210/small/1512910432_40e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171210%2Fsmall%2F1512910432_40e1.jpg&h=7b7e5977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新娘汪小姐表示，自己在12月3日舉行婚禮。惟看到場地的佈置，認為根本不值3.6萬元。據現場影片和相片看，當日台上擺放一個用上白布和白花的帳幕，而配合綠色和紫色的燈光，難免予人一種陰森氣氛，如同靈堂一般。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171211/57562777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57562777&d=OZLboJ8a3aGlrRIfUsiPBE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=02dcc275\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57562777&h=116aa7f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171211/57562777</a><br />\n<br />\n梨視頻"}]}